      <br><abbr title="Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency">DVLA</abbr>
      <br>Swansea
      <br>SA99 1ZZ
      <br>
    </p>

    <p class="lbh-body-m">Don’t use these details for general enquiries - contact DVLA instead.</p>
